# CODEOWNERS — DocuBook Monorepo
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Order matters: last matching pattern wins.
# Each owner must be a GitHub user/team with READ access to the repo.

# ── Global fallback ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                               @DocuBook/maintainers

# ── CI / GitHub configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/                        @DocuBook/maintainers

# ── Packages ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
packages/cli/                   @DocuBook/maintainers
packages/core/                  @DocuBook/maintainers

# ── Apps ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
apps/                           @DocuBook/maintainers

# ── Workspace config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
pnpm-workspace.yaml             @DocuBook/maintainers
turbo.json                      @DocuBook/maintainers
package.json                    @DocuBook/maintainers
tsconfig.json                   @DocuBook/maintainers
